snippet.title: Legend of the Master Baiter - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Embark on a new adventure as you work to uncover the legend of the goddess of Inzu! Catch 50 different fish, fill up your aquariums, and help the people of Inzu in this unique fishing RPG!

Legend of the Master Baiter on Kagura Games Store: https://www.kaguragames.com/product/legend-of-the-master-baiter/
